{"tid":1384550,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[Medic 醫療兵］識急救，愛發夢既香港人同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:58:49.000Z","uid":59059,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"944f489d73710f5cdf41a35f472dd5c76b6296bc","tid":1384550,"uid":59059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"兩個月以黎既抗爭<br />\n面對極權政府既打壓，黑警濫捕濫暴<br />\n由警棍盾牌，發展到濫射催淚彈，甚至真槍實彈<br />\n無差別咁攻擊，圍捕！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">甚至現在連消防救護都要黑警批準先可以入示威區救人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n場仗仲有排打！<br />\n<br />\n除左物資既支援<br />\n希望發起一眾有急救知識既同路人backup前線！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">I WANT YOU</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係呀！係你呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n和理非又想行多一步<br />\n家人擔心你上前線危險<br />\n<br />\n同佢地講：「我去救人！」<br />\n<br />\n救得一個，得一個！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十字為記</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔係維記</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/epejRL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FepejRL6.png&h=5ec6083e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(想自己設計logo但有心無力🤦🏼&zwj;♂️攪得成再算)<br />\n<br />\n引述：<br />\n<br />\n「醫療兵是前線戰場上救死扶傷的主要力量，他們有着無人可比的仁慈與愛心，在戰場上不管是敵是友他們都會給予援助，在戰爭中沒有任何立場，在工作中也沒有任何怨言，他們永遠會盡全力的去拯救每一條受傷的生命。那麼在戰爭中究竟能不能攻擊醫療兵呢？這個問題在國際公約上的答案很明確&mdash;&mdash;不能！日內瓦公約上明確規定了任何時間，任何地點醫療兵不能作為任何人的攻擊目標。更何況醫療兵在戰場上是完全無威脅的，他們所做的救死扶傷也是高尚的，所以一般只要是有榮譽感，秩序感和正義感的士兵都是不會殺害這些醫療兵的。」<br />\n<br />\n做medic記得做好防護裝備<br />\n配備大量急救物資（唔多講，盡帶），乾糧，甚至各種coupon（身體同心靈上支援）<br />\n俾狗查，俾狗捉，大條道理去救人<br />\n因為警員失信，無差別攻擊市民，所以我地要出分力<br />\n<br />\n「香港🇭🇰，唔再係一個地區，而係一班人！」<br />\n<br />\n「我地就係香港！」<br />\n<br />\n如果支持既幫推<br />\n<br />\n我地戰場上見！"},{"pid":"9446b0585659dc61aa48fbf381b337ea28df170a","tid":1384550,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:08:45.000Z","msg":"Battlefield?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"6e3f93b7db4666ee545f901419e6fcca41bee163","tid":1384550,"uid":258473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:10:02.000Z","msg":"Count me in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a64c66388a470d3be11eceddcefd5c51229a72","tid":1384550,"uid":59059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9446b0585659dc61aa48fbf381b337ea28df170a","tid":1384550,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:08:45.000Z","msg":"Battlefield?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"多謝！我只想出一分力！<br />\n<br />\n香港示威區已經離戰場不遠......"},{"pid":"08fc5cfe3b57688bd35749b22a337dd9a2ee28b0","tid":1384550,"uid":59059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e3f93b7db4666ee545f901419e6fcca41bee163","tid":1384550,"uid":258473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:10:02.000Z","msg":"Count me in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:11:32.000Z","msg":"大家搵（十字logo）貼頭盔又好，做pin掛手臂都好"},{"pid":"6a50d6b43e6f4aa48cbbafe0ec0ddf1ff1a04eb3","tid":1384550,"uid":276191,"like"